    <mods:abstract>Arkham Horror is an adventure board game based on the works of H.P. Lovecraft, designed to be played cooperatively from between one to eight players. In it, the players each take on the role of one pre-generated adventurer as they move through the fictional town of Arkham, Massachusetts in an attempt to close portals to otherwordly planes of existence. Originally published by Chaosium in 1987, this descriptions refers to the 2005 revised reprint.
    </mods:abstract>
